---
layout: page.njk
title: home
pagination:
  data: collections.posts
  size: 2
  alias: posts
templateEngineOverride: njk, md
---
<div class="container">
  <h2>about me</h2>
  {% snippet %}

  Hi! I'm a front-end developer, and here are some of the things I've made, thought about, and played with.

  {% image "/images/self.jpg", "a picture of me", "snippet-image" %}

  {% endsnippet %}
</div>

<div class="container">
  <h2>recent posts</h2>
  {% snippet %}
  {% if posts %}
  {% for post in posts %}
  - [{{ post.data.title }}]({{ post.url }})

  {{ post.data.excerpt }}
  {% endfor %}
  {% else %}
  No posts yet!
  {% endif %}
  {% endsnippet %}
</div>